query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('architecture',
'c++',
'gm-techniques',
'object-oriented') AND s.site_name IN ('rpg',
'softwareengineering')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 1 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Citizen Patrol',
'Famous Question',
'Necromancer',
'Nice Question',
'Peer Pressure',
'Tumbleweed',
'Yearling');
